{"tid":87052,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[正經] 藥劑去向問一問 (Monash & QUT)","createTime":"2017-01-19T13:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T09:50:50.000Z","uid":77693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fee25a1271006c383b49df93a7cb3c0b6d06bbf5","tid":87052,"uid":77693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T13:38:52.000Z","msg":"我係真心想讀藥劑的傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家係QUT pharmacy 剛剛讀完year 1<br />\n我知香港競爭十分大 而我真係想讀好後返香港醫院做<br />\n我知monash 新開左個Bachelor加Master of Pharmacy的新開combined programme<br />\n依家我有個offer 係手但問題係<br />\n1.冇任何的credit 可以攞到<br />\n2.未知Master of Pharmacy (Monash course 包了) 同 Master of Clinical Pharmacy (QUT 畢業後會讀)， 對未來在醫院發展有咩分別，以我所知 Master of Pharmacy 已在某些職位中已足夠<br />\n3.在藥劑師註冊名冊只見一個係QUT pharmacy 出身，相反Monash 有71個，有冇師兄明白係少人係QUT 讀，定課程cover 得唔夠令佢地考唔到？<br />\n4.QUT 出身同Monash 出身係香港醫院嘅人眼中是否一視同仁? (前題佢地都考到牌)<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇師兄係香港醫院or任何有關藥劑的崗位做緊呢？<br />\n<br />\n希望有人幫到我決定繼續上year 2 or 去monash 讀新5年課程<br />\n<br />\nMany thanks 各位巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401be1ed6dca251336ce5303d4e29f8a4af63387","tid":87052,"uid":77693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:29:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fb6f9c215e131bfad7921efb69bb63d406e3ebf","tid":87052,"uid":15690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T15:06:11.000Z","msg":"外國讀完就唔好返香港做喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a335d4c1d9140a24417ac1728300cdd51f41aa5c","tid":87052,"uid":77693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T15:28:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>外國讀完就唔好返香港做喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最少希望有個機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3dce9d08a90db6a1783db992326b6b09956ca67","tid":87052,"uid":34206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T00:39:33.000Z","msg":"依家香港醫管局自己都收唔晒HKU, CUHK graduates, 你係澳洲讀完返香港只會死路一條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ff8994efe23571a9b2a468e036917301db06c1","tid":87052,"uid":15690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T02:30:56.000Z","msg":"HA 既 RP 都唔係個個升到P，香港既Pharm 條路好難行，如果做HA 既就更加奴隸，醫藥唔分家跟本無得玩，後悔當年貪快唔讀醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f7e3090f502e7f6a60868de379d8338897ff1b","tid":87052,"uid":77693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:28:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家香港醫管局自己都收唔晒HKU, CUHK graduates, 你係澳洲讀完返香港只會死路一條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n若果再讀多少少，例如Master 咁有冇可能？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b70aa589e5342880c07ea5055cf1e3dbcd12e59","tid":87052,"uid":77693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>HA 既 RP 都唔係個個升到P，香港既Pharm 條路好難行，如果做HA 既就更加奴隸，醫藥唔分家跟本無得玩，後悔當年貪快唔讀醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽講立法會傾緊，但不知要傾幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n師兄你最後做唔做到RP?"},{"pid":"12fd3666f3547537cd2be165797597a2698b269f","tid":87052,"uid":47153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:38:19.000Z","msg":"點解唔喺澳洲做？"},{"pid":"5a011fbe2dc22053ff290e238142b9f71d42a847","tid":87052,"uid":896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:42:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>HA 既 RP 都唔係個個升到P，香港既Pharm 條路好難行，如果做HA 既就更加奴隸，醫藥唔分家跟本無得玩，後悔當年貪快唔讀醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /