<br />\nHA 做過intern 實好d , 就算外國番尼都最好係外國有 hospital experience...community pharmacy experience 依家HA好似唔多睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師兄意思係睇經驗多過學歷？事關一間全球第四依家呢間28x <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重考慮緊轉唔轉校</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHA 來講，經驗應該重要過學校，有d外國番尼既pharm係外國做開某d service，甘岩HA有醫院想launch依d service佢地就吃香了 畢竟香港pharmacy比外國落後"},{"pid":"65af3708efef3c2b85eacf13bb6d2c5a91736fa7","tid":87052,"uid":77693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T03:28:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHA 做過intern 實好d , 就算外國番尼都最好係外國有 hospital experience...community pharmacy experience 依家HA好似唔多睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師兄意思係睇經驗多過學歷？事關一間全球第四依家呢間28x <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重考慮緊轉唔轉校</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHA 來講，經驗應該重要過學校，有d外國番尼既pharm係外國做開某d service，甘岩HA有醫院想launch依d service佢地就吃香了 畢竟香港pharmacy比外國落後</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好好，唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35913b498503cb70f21d34b4bac026fb78f9476","tid":87052,"uid":70007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:45:08.000Z","msg":"做HA 真係做到隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申RP"},{"pid":"5a01a6e60bd8ba5a8f848425f18a0ab21bfe21b1","tid":87052,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:21:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f72faa9dc051f3576424dec2d85efaa2a056f57","tid":87052,"uid":77693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T09:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做HA 真係做到隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申RP</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師兄你覺得佢地收人多睇d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2cb63cfcd520878210bc1e63f5b07ae24bbdd7","tid":87052,"uid":77693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0